fields.headline: Corrections and clarifications
fields.bodyText: • The caption on a photograph of Sumire Nakamura said that she will become the youngest professional player of the board game Go when she makes her debut in April, aged 10, but omitted to name the other person in the picture. The figure on the left was the award-winning professional Go player Yuta Iyama (Ready, set …, 7 January, page 29).
